      "notes": "Step 1 of 3 for carousel upload. Step 2: PUT the PDF binary to the uploadUrl returned here. Step 3: Create ugcPost with the asset URN. For Cycle 1, use a PDF generated from the slide copy — Canva exports to PDF natively."
    }
